WEBVTT

01:40.460 --> 01:45.940
[Speed and Love]

01:46.280 --> 01:48.850
[Episode 2]

01:51.360 --> 01:52.280
This is for you.

01:53.080 --> 01:54.280
When I come back,

01:55.940 --> 01:57.870
I'll check how your handwriting's

01:58.289 --> 01:59.500
coming along.

02:00.580 --> 02:02.580
Keep practicing your handwriting.

02:03.020 --> 02:04.880
And don't be picky with your food.

02:05.140 --> 02:05.890
Zhao.

02:07.680 --> 02:09.520
Will you come back to see me?

02:10.160 --> 02:12.410
Will you always think of me?

02:13.690 --> 02:14.410
I will.

02:15.650 --> 02:17.180
As long as you don't change,

02:18.880 --> 02:20.350
I won't change either.

02:24.250 --> 02:26.510
Zhao, it's been so long since you called.

02:27.160 --> 02:29.160
I don't know how to reach you,

02:29.620 --> 02:31.500
so I can only try to write to you.

02:32.180 --> 02:33.900
I hope you'll receive this.

02:34.380 --> 02:35.980
Mom and I are moving.

02:37.130 --> 02:38.790
Once I know where we're going,

02:39.010 --> 02:40.340
I'll write to you again.

02:40.970 --> 02:42.620
Miss you. Mu.

02:46.160 --> 02:46.810
Zhao,

02:47.560 --> 02:50.160
Mom and I
have finally moved into our new house.

02:50.370 --> 02:52.230
I really wish you could come back.

02:52.920 --> 02:55.170
I'll be starting middle school next year.

02:55.170 --> 02:57.900
I'll have lots of homework
and tutoring classes.

02:58.180 --> 02:59.530
If I do well on my exams,

03:00.020 --> 03:01.390
will you come back to see me

03:01.390 --> 03:03.720
during the summer break after graduation?

03:03.720 --> 03:05.230
Miss you. Mu.

03:10.350 --> 03:11.190
Zhao,

03:11.850 --> 03:14.130
this is the last time I'm writing to you,

03:14.960 --> 03:17.070
because you never wrote me back,

03:17.940 --> 03:20.340
and I feel like
I've been writing to the air.

03:21.130 --> 03:22.990
I'm starting middle school soon.

03:23.180 --> 03:24.910
I'll have many new classmates,

03:25.690 --> 03:27.570
and I'll make more friends.

03:28.410 --> 03:29.300
So,

03:29.970 --> 03:30.940
that's it.

03:31.690 --> 03:33.460
I won't miss you anymore. Mu.

03:42.410 --> 03:44.020
I won't be at the shop tomorrow.

03:44.020 --> 03:45.460
If it's urgent, ask Yang.

03:46.900 --> 03:47.530
Yes.

03:49.740 --> 03:51.740
I must go there tomorrow afternoon.

03:54.180 --> 03:55.380
I know what I'm doing.

03:58.560 --> 03:59.820
Alright, don't worry.

04:03.560 --> 04:04.420
I'm hanging up.

04:12.000 --> 04:13.640
Where are you sleeping tonight?

04:13.640 --> 04:15.500
You go to sleep. I'll leave later.

04:16.940 --> 04:18.600
Do you have somewhere to stay?

04:29.770 --> 04:31.100
Mind your own business.

04:34.300 --> 04:35.130
Goodbye.

04:51.840 --> 04:52.950
Wait, Yang, are you

04:52.980 --> 04:55.190
grilling skewers just to avoid drinking?

04:55.190 --> 04:56.950
No. The fire's a bit too strong.

04:56.970 --> 04:59.210
-I have to watch it.
-Don't burn it.

04:59.530 --> 05:00.770
[Wan Qing]

05:00.180 --> 05:01.810
I'll make it up to you later.

05:07.730 --> 05:09.730
Something's going on tonight, huh?

05:10.250 --> 05:11.810
Your phone's been busy.

05:12.010 --> 05:13.330
A new girlfriend?

05:16.860 --> 05:17.660
Just drink.

05:17.860 --> 05:19.570
Drink while you can!

05:19.600 --> 05:20.770
See? That's why I said

05:20.770 --> 05:22.370
Jin, you're still the worst.

05:23.250 --> 05:24.710
Eat up. I've got more here.

05:26.570 --> 05:27.030
Come on.

05:27.040 --> 05:27.430
Come on.

05:27.430 --> 05:27.940
Cheers.

05:28.210 --> 05:29.420
Come on, let's drink.

06:03.340 --> 06:04.330
You beat him up.

06:04.980 --> 06:06.440
That's not fair, Brother.

06:06.470 --> 06:07.860
We didn't lay a finger on him.

06:07.860 --> 06:09.540
He accidentally tripped

06:09.540 --> 06:10.690
He bumped and fell.

06:10.860 --> 06:11.490
Is that so?

06:13.610 --> 06:14.940
I've brought the money.

06:15.400 --> 06:16.660
I'm taking him with me.

06:25.460 --> 06:27.190
Why didn't you answer my calls?

06:27.960 --> 06:29.760
I'll bring the rest another day.

06:29.980 --> 06:31.370
I called you over a dozen times,

06:31.370 --> 06:32.659
and you didn't pick up once.

06:32.659 --> 06:34.100
If there's nothing else, I'll be going.

06:34.100 --> 06:36.230
Don't play such childish games again.

06:37.620 --> 06:39.940
I hired the best chef from Diya City

06:40.100 --> 06:42.130
and spent 5 hours on makeup and hair.

06:42.450 --> 06:43.300
Even for my father's second wedding,

06:43.300 --> 06:45.159
I didn't put this much effort
into dressing.

06:45.159 --> 06:47.480
You're leaving without even taking a look?

06:47.480 --> 06:48.880
You're not allowed to go.

06:51.430 --> 06:52.159
I took a look.

06:53.380 --> 06:54.330
Can I go now?

06:58.560 --> 06:59.320
Jin Zhao,

07:00.280 --> 07:01.140
how about this?

07:01.840 --> 07:03.440
Stay and have dinner with me,

07:04.340 --> 07:06.060
and I'll write off all of Jin Qiang's

07:06.060 --> 07:06.940
gambling debt.

07:07.970 --> 07:08.830
What do you say?

07:21.240 --> 07:22.150
Just one meal?

07:22.630 --> 07:23.680
Stay with me

07:23.880 --> 07:25.080
after dinner.

07:25.960 --> 07:28.160
And what exactly would I be staying for?

07:31.020 --> 07:32.170
For...

07:39.860 --> 07:40.860
Are you asleep?

07:50.350 --> 07:52.350
I have something to do. I'm leaving.

07:53.540 --> 07:54.530
You're abandoning your father?

07:54.530 --> 07:55.390
He's yours now.

07:58.400 --> 07:59.130
It's late.

07:59.340 --> 08:00.200
Go to sleep now.

08:03.480 --> 08:05.080
Will you come back tomorrow?

08:39.110 --> 08:40.350
You took the gift?

08:40.890 --> 08:41.940
Did you open it?

08:43.610 --> 08:44.450
You're up?

08:46.180 --> 08:48.110
Why are you spacing out? Come here.

08:48.310 --> 08:49.400
I made you something to eat.

08:49.400 --> 08:51.200
Have some food before you go out.

08:51.400 --> 08:52.170
Mrs. Zhao,

08:52.560 --> 08:54.290
do you know where Jin Zhao went?

08:54.490 --> 08:56.150
Do you need him for something?

08:56.540 --> 08:57.660
I'm just asking.

08:58.610 --> 08:59.850
He's busy outside.

09:00.490 --> 09:02.970
He usually doesn't come home?

09:03.210 --> 09:05.070
There's nothing going on at home.

09:05.090 --> 09:06.210
Why would he come back?

09:06.210 --> 09:06.810
Hurry.

09:09.540 --> 09:11.070
I'll go take a shower first.

09:35.490 --> 09:36.850
There's nothing going on at home.

09:36.850 --> 09:38.110
Why would he come back?

10:06.000 --> 10:06.880
Mrs. Zhao,

10:07.270 --> 10:08.800
the water heater is broken.

10:24.710 --> 10:25.510
What's wrong?

10:28.370 --> 10:29.090
This...

10:29.430 --> 10:31.210
What's happening? The water...

10:31.210 --> 10:32.760
How did the water heater

10:32.920 --> 10:34.010
suddenly break?

10:35.650 --> 10:37.370
I can't fix this.

10:38.710 --> 10:39.950
How did this happen?

10:40.670 --> 10:41.550
Don't panic.

10:45.120 --> 10:46.120
Where are you?

10:46.650 --> 10:48.490
The pipe on the water heater at home
fell off.

10:48.490 --> 10:49.950
Hurry back and take a look.

10:50.090 --> 10:51.140
If the water floods downstairs,

10:51.140 --> 10:53.040
they'll come up and give us trouble.

10:53.040 --> 10:54.490
I don't know how to fix it.

10:57.380 --> 10:58.180
Mrs. Zhao.

10:58.850 --> 10:59.540
Why don't we

10:59.820 --> 11:01.020
ask Jin Zhao to fix it?

12:04.450 --> 12:05.780
What are you looking at?

12:06.450 --> 12:07.420
The sun.

12:10.520 --> 12:12.450
Looking at the sun in the bathroom?

12:17.330 --> 12:18.330
Did you fix it?

12:20.450 --> 12:21.170
Xin,

12:21.660 --> 12:22.720
what are you doing?

12:23.580 --> 12:24.840
Looking at the sun too?

12:25.430 --> 12:26.560
Go back to your room.

12:28.100 --> 12:28.770
How is it?

12:29.140 --> 12:30.360
The water has stopped,

12:30.360 --> 12:31.620
but the pipe is broken.

12:31.940 --> 12:32.940
What should we do?

12:33.300 --> 12:34.600
The water heater is too old.

12:34.600 --> 12:35.240
It's hard to find a replacement pipe.

12:35.240 --> 12:36.570
Let's just get a new one.

12:36.660 --> 12:38.180
Why spend money on that?

12:38.400 --> 12:39.920
Find a way to reconnect it.

12:39.970 --> 12:41.030
As long as it works.

12:41.640 --> 12:42.380
I'll order a new one.

12:42.380 --> 12:43.330
Sanlai will come to install it.

12:43.330 --> 12:44.530
Don't worry about it.

12:47.270 --> 12:48.570
Xin, why are you standing here?

12:48.570 --> 12:49.300
Come on.

12:50.040 --> 12:51.050
Go mind your own business.

12:51.050 --> 12:51.850
Come quickly.

12:58.610 --> 13:00.270
Well, when can I take a shower?

13:01.180 --> 13:02.380
Once it's installed.

13:02.410 --> 13:03.870
When will it be installed?

13:05.090 --> 13:07.090
Sanlai will come to install it soon.

13:07.250 --> 13:08.660
Someone else is going to install it?

13:08.660 --> 13:09.520
What about you?

13:09.570 --> 13:10.370
I have something to do.

13:10.370 --> 13:11.160
What is it?

13:12.230 --> 13:14.090
Why do you have so many questions?

13:44.400 --> 13:45.440
Hello. Hello.

13:45.720 --> 13:47.000
Go, follow him.

13:48.210 --> 13:48.790
Get in!

13:48.810 --> 13:49.450
Thank you.

14:20.420 --> 14:22.020
Hello. How can I help you?

14:23.920 --> 14:25.650
This one. This one. I want this.

15:12.530 --> 15:14.530
Please wait at platform 1.

15:14.810 --> 15:16.610
Thank you for your cooperation.

15:36.360 --> 15:37.760
Why are you following me?

15:38.850 --> 15:40.910
What a coincidence. You're here too.

15:40.920 --> 15:42.380
I'm shopping around here.

15:43.020 --> 15:44.620
Weren't you going shopping?

15:44.660 --> 15:45.720
The internet says there's an event
on Thursday

15:45.720 --> 15:46.900
with lots of handsome guys.

15:46.900 --> 15:48.430
It's only Wednesday today.

15:51.680 --> 15:52.890
What do you think of this banana?

15:52.890 --> 15:54.040
It looks sweet.

15:54.720 --> 15:56.920
Do you need a fruit knife to eat a banana?

16:01.270 --> 16:03.090
Didn't you just buy it from the store?

16:03.090 --> 16:04.210
I'm planning to

16:04.300 --> 16:05.630
buy a watermelon later.

16:08.500 --> 16:10.290
Bananas and watermelons are both good.

16:10.290 --> 16:11.520
Buy yourself something to eat and drink.

16:11.520 --> 16:12.580
Stop following me.

16:15.480 --> 16:16.780
I'll tell you one more time—

16:16.780 --> 16:17.840
stop following me.

16:35.910 --> 16:36.580
Hello.

16:37.120 --> 16:38.080
Here, please.

16:38.280 --> 16:39.160
300.

16:39.400 --> 16:40.130
100.

16:40.250 --> 16:41.610
200.

16:43.160 --> 16:44.400
-100, please.
-No, no, no.

16:44.400 --> 16:45.850
-200, 200.
-100.

16:46.520 --> 16:47.360
Stop here.

16:51.270 --> 16:53.400
Scamming people for money again, huh?

16:53.920 --> 16:55.520
Aren't you Brandy's sister?

16:55.730 --> 16:56.720
What are you doing here?

16:56.720 --> 16:57.850
Where are you going?

16:59.090 --> 17:00.370
Jin Zhao and I made an appointment.

17:00.370 --> 17:01.830
I'm just going to find him.

17:02.740 --> 17:03.470
Now?

17:04.240 --> 17:05.450
He really allowed you to go?

17:05.450 --> 17:06.140
Yes.

17:06.170 --> 17:08.700
Jin,
did you make an appointment with him too?

17:08.960 --> 17:10.160
I was just about to go.

17:11.760 --> 17:13.560
Perfect. Let's go together.

17:14.020 --> 17:15.349
I was going to take a cab,

17:15.369 --> 17:17.099
but I didn't bring enough cash.

17:17.710 --> 17:18.880
He really said you could come?

17:18.880 --> 17:20.490
Look, we're running out of time.

17:20.490 --> 17:21.369
You brought enough cash, right?

17:21.369 --> 17:22.369
I'll get on first.

17:23.800 --> 17:24.480
To Peita.

17:43.120 --> 17:44.760
Quick! Don't stop!

17:53.210 --> 17:54.970
Beat him!

18:01.850 --> 18:03.380
Good!
Don't give him a chance to fight back!

18:03.380 --> 18:05.440
Don't give him a chance to fight back!

18:06.620 --> 18:08.050
Yes! Yes! Yes!

18:09.000 --> 18:11.000
Count! Count! Count!

18:11.030 --> 18:12.320
Five!

18:12.430 --> 18:13.510
Four!

18:13.860 --> 18:14.970
Three!

18:15.060 --> 18:16.220
Two!

18:16.460 --> 18:17.380
One!

18:19.770 --> 18:20.490
Uncle,

18:20.550 --> 18:21.980
you were right. We won!

18:25.440 --> 18:27.040
That was just the appetizer.

18:27.070 --> 18:28.930
The real show hasn't started yet.

18:29.470 --> 18:30.450
In the next match,

18:30.450 --> 18:31.340
He Zhang

18:32.080 --> 18:33.610
will give Brandy a beating!

18:38.220 --> 18:39.630
Who's his opponent?

18:40.140 --> 18:41.580
Someone works for Wan Shengbang.

18:41.580 --> 18:42.530
His name is He Zhang,

18:42.530 --> 18:43.990
and he seems pretty tough.

18:45.820 --> 18:46.620
Yes, tough.

18:47.970 --> 18:49.250
I've seen him fight.

18:49.900 --> 18:51.050
He won't lose.

19:03.980 --> 19:06.310
Don't miss the mountain roads
in Qingshi.

19:06.720 --> 19:07.850
You'll still have to

19:08.190 --> 19:09.920
keep playing along with Wan's.

19:11.720 --> 19:13.410
Sorry to put you through this match.

19:13.410 --> 19:14.070
Be careful.

19:14.210 --> 19:15.010
Try not to hurt

19:15.240 --> 19:16.300
your hands or legs.

19:17.490 --> 19:18.690
I know what I'm doing.

19:58.570 --> 19:59.900
Ready to take a beating?

20:06.570 --> 20:07.920
Lin Sui raised the bet.

20:17.030 --> 20:18.510
Wan's raised the bet.

20:20.750 --> 20:22.860
Dad, how could you raise the bet?

20:23.140 --> 20:24.800
What if something goes wrong?

20:25.970 --> 20:26.860
Qing,

20:27.340 --> 20:29.210
are you worried about He Zhang

20:29.530 --> 20:30.640
or about Brandy?

20:31.890 --> 20:34.170
You just love stirring up trouble,
don't you?

20:34.170 --> 20:36.170
If you don't want to watch, get lost.

20:59.290 --> 21:00.050
He Zhang.

21:00.940 --> 21:02.310
If you dare hurt him,

21:02.550 --> 21:03.510
you're dead.

21:03.720 --> 21:05.320
You care about him that much?

21:05.370 --> 21:06.500
He's my man.

21:30.440 --> 21:31.440
Go home!

21:55.460 --> 21:57.020
Don't disappoint me.

22:13.830 --> 22:15.490
Bite down on your mouthguard.

22:16.340 --> 22:17.660
Okay, hands.

22:19.840 --> 22:21.280
No jewelry or hard objects allowed.

22:21.280 --> 22:22.880
Good. Now show me your hands.

22:25.240 --> 22:26.000
Listen to me.

22:26.100 --> 22:28.630
No strikes to the back of the head
or the spine.

22:30.600 --> 22:31.460
Fight!

22:39.050 --> 22:40.330
Not bad, Zhang!

22:41.020 --> 22:42.820
Beat him! Remember!

22:54.690 --> 22:55.730
Get up, He Zhang!

23:22.920 --> 23:24.610
Sorry to put you through this match.

23:24.610 --> 23:26.120
You'll still have to keep playing along

23:26.120 --> 23:27.390
with Wan's.

23:33.450 --> 23:34.100
Come on!

24:04.820 --> 24:05.610
Stop, stop.

24:06.100 --> 24:06.860
Who is she?

24:07.490 --> 24:08.550
She's with Brandy.

24:10.220 --> 24:12.270
Come on, who is she?

24:12.920 --> 24:14.200
She has wine.
Please.

24:18.630 --> 24:19.670
Do me a favor.

24:20.690 --> 24:21.450
Okay.

24:22.570 --> 24:23.240
Let's go.

24:24.540 --> 24:25.690
Brandy is Jin Zhao?

24:26.750 --> 24:29.030
Why do you all call him Brandy?

24:29.780 --> 24:31.500
Isn't there a Chinese saying?

24:32.720 --> 24:34.810
"Drink while you can?"

24:35.050 --> 24:35.720
Smart.

24:38.030 --> 24:39.340
They only let familiar faces in;

24:39.340 --> 24:40.940
strangers can't get inside.

24:41.530 --> 24:42.530
Stop, stop, stop.

24:43.490 --> 24:44.530
Okay, okay, okay.

24:59.810 --> 25:00.810
Where is Jin Zhao?

25:02.340 --> 25:03.060
In the ring.

25:23.810 --> 25:25.200
Let's go, sis.

25:25.530 --> 25:26.660
Don't let him see you.

25:26.660 --> 25:27.920
He'll get distracted.

25:29.450 --> 25:30.860
Make way, please.

25:30.970 --> 25:31.560
Okay.

25:36.100 --> 25:37.340
Brandy.

25:37.620 --> 25:38.900
Take him down!

25:42.830 --> 25:43.970
What?

25:44.450 --> 25:45.970
Lin bet on Brandy,

25:46.140 --> 25:47.730
and Wan bet on He Zhang?

25:48.670 --> 25:49.600
Who are they?

25:51.490 --> 25:53.820
That guy in red over there

25:54.010 --> 25:54.860
is Lin.

25:55.210 --> 25:56.550
He's the owner of this place

25:56.550 --> 25:57.950
and the banker for today.

25:58.830 --> 26:00.360
That old man sitting across

26:00.610 --> 26:02.340
is the owner of Wan's Auto Shop—

26:02.610 --> 26:04.640
half the garages here belong to him.

26:05.270 --> 26:06.590
The blond guy

26:07.030 --> 26:08.580
is the local boxing champion.

26:08.580 --> 26:09.860
Ten times the stakes.

26:10.180 --> 26:11.340
That's insane!

26:11.570 --> 26:13.100
Is he trying to kill Brandy?

26:13.290 --> 26:13.970
Well...

26:14.870 --> 26:16.270
can't we just call it off?

26:16.480 --> 26:18.000
Let's get Jin Zhao out of here.

26:18.000 --> 26:19.810
Of course not, sis.

26:20.290 --> 26:21.820
Everyone here has already placed bets.

26:21.820 --> 26:23.610
Once you're in the ring,
your fate is in the hands of heaven.

26:23.610 --> 26:25.260
What about the money?
Are you going to pay it back?

26:25.260 --> 26:26.100
I'll pay.

26:26.600 --> 26:27.670
I have money.

26:27.970 --> 26:29.530
There's money in my bank account.

26:29.530 --> 26:31.530
If I pay, can the fight be called off?

28:04.850 --> 28:05.720
Jin.
Hit him!

28:05.900 --> 28:06.940
Jin Zhao!

28:17.610 --> 28:18.300
Beat him!

28:23.810 --> 28:24.700
Stop! Stop!

28:36.390 --> 28:38.430
Get up, Brandy! Bro!

28:45.790 --> 28:46.470
Jin Zhao!

28:46.490 --> 28:48.770
Count the seconds, ref! Count the seconds!

28:48.770 --> 28:49.690
Jin Zhao!

28:57.620 --> 28:59.620
Get up! Get up!

29:07.010 --> 29:08.010
Jin Zhao!

29:16.980 --> 29:18.020
Eight!

29:18.620 --> 29:19.490
Seven!

29:19.940 --> 29:20.860
Six!

29:21.180 --> 29:22.180
Five!

29:22.660 --> 29:23.690
Four!

29:23.970 --> 29:25.010
Three!

29:25.210 --> 29:26.210
Two!

29:26.600 --> 29:27.630
One!

29:34.500 --> 29:35.220
Sis!

29:45.290 --> 29:46.050
Are you okay?

29:46.450 --> 29:47.170
Okay?

29:50.540 --> 29:51.260
Fight!

30:01.070 --> 30:01.900
Zhao!

30:07.050 --> 30:07.680
Brother!

30:37.220 --> 30:39.450
♪ Make it fast, never slow down ♪

30:39.480 --> 30:41.950
♪ Show off my extraordinary form ♪

30:41.980 --> 30:43.090
♪ Speeding love ♪

30:43.120 --> 30:44.510
♪ Whether I succeed or fail ♪

30:44.540 --> 30:46.690
♪ I just want to be free ♪

30:46.710 --> 30:49.270
♪ Shining star, heart on fire ♪

30:49.300 --> 30:51.550
♪ The odds of winning are 100% ♪

30:51.570 --> 30:54.390
♪ Make my name be known
throughout the world ♪

30:54.410 --> 30:56.490
♪ You just wait and see ♪

30:56.520 --> 30:58.890
♪ Make it fast, never slow down ♪

30:58.920 --> 31:00.970
♪ Show off my extraordinary form ♪

30:59.940 --> 31:00.730
Come with me

31:00.990 --> 31:02.390
♪ Speeding love ♪

31:02.410 --> 31:03.640
♪ Whether I succeed or fail ♪

31:03.660 --> 31:05.840
♪ I just want to be free ♪

31:05.870 --> 31:08.430
♪ Shining star, heart on fire ♪

31:07.580 --> 31:08.820
We're not done yet

31:08.460 --> 31:10.760
♪ The odds of winning are 100% ♪

31:10.790 --> 31:13.250
♪ Make my name be known
throughout the world ♪

31:13.210 --> 31:14.180
Who is this woman?

31:13.280 --> 31:15.610
♪ You just wait and see ♪

31:15.790 --> 31:16.850
She's my relative.

31:18.220 --> 31:19.880
Who are you trying to deceive?

31:20.270 --> 31:21.750
I heard her call Jin Zhao.

31:21.990 --> 31:23.280
No, she didn't.

31:23.750 --> 31:25.310
You misheard, Miss.

31:27.570 --> 31:28.570
Be honest with me.

31:29.280 --> 31:30.950
Is she Jin Zhao's new girl?

31:31.600 --> 31:33.000
How could that be possible?

31:33.000 --> 31:34.330
You know him.

31:34.500 --> 31:36.100
He's not interested in this.

31:39.490 --> 31:40.660
You idiot!

31:40.860 --> 31:41.660
Moron!

31:42.600 --> 31:43.630
I'm telling you.

31:44.080 --> 31:46.120
Tonight we must teach him a lesson!

32:11.210 --> 32:13.070
How did you know about this place?

32:13.970 --> 32:15.030
Who brought you in?

32:15.660 --> 32:16.590
You're injured.

32:16.640 --> 32:17.730
Answer me first.

32:18.260 --> 32:20.120
How did you know about this place?

32:24.690 --> 32:25.690
I got beaten.

32:26.670 --> 32:27.730
Why are you crying?

32:28.690 --> 32:30.410
You weren't like this before.

32:38.360 --> 32:39.420
It's getting late.

32:39.580 --> 32:40.640
I'll take you back.

32:55.360 --> 32:56.030
Go home.

32:56.250 --> 32:57.690
It'll be fine once you're home.
I'll book your ticket.

32:57.690 --> 32:58.860
I'm not going back.

33:00.930 --> 33:01.890
Why not?

33:03.340 --> 33:04.300
Now that you're here

33:04.300 --> 33:05.760
and have seen everything,

33:07.330 --> 33:08.990
what else is there to stay for?

33:09.450 --> 33:12.140
Why did you become like this?

33:42.660 --> 33:44.980
I heard everything Sanlai said to you

33:46.670 --> 33:48.130
in the stairwell that day.

33:48.970 --> 33:52.170
He said you were going to do something
life-threatening.

33:53.250 --> 33:54.910
Do you think it's ridiculous?

33:56.660 --> 33:58.080
Do you find it hard to understand

33:58.080 --> 34:00.320
why I care so much about your affairs?

34:03.050 --> 34:04.340
Maybe in your eyes,

34:05.580 --> 34:07.510
I'm just your childhood playmate,

34:08.650 --> 34:09.850
Coming here this time

34:10.170 --> 34:11.530
was just for fun.

34:11.620 --> 34:12.889
After the trip, I would leave

34:12.889 --> 34:14.620
and have nothing to do with you.

34:20.199 --> 34:21.000
That's right.

34:25.110 --> 34:26.590
How could you understand?

34:29.130 --> 34:30.900
If you could, you wouldn't have

34:33.120 --> 34:34.260
stayed away for all these years

34:33.520 --> 34:36.630
♪ I leave after your curtain call ♪

34:34.260 --> 34:36.460
without coming back to see me even once.

34:39.330 --> 34:42.530
♪ I ask the tired bird ♪

34:39.820 --> 34:41.820
I wrote you so many letters.

34:42.699 --> 34:44.420
You never replied,

34:43.320 --> 34:46.380
♪ About your news ♪

34:44.780 --> 34:46.010
Not a single letter

34:48.639 --> 34:52.290
♪ You're too serious in
both your passion and silence ♪

34:49.449 --> 34:51.310
I waited for you for so many years—

34:52.330 --> 34:53.860
the first summer vacation,

34:54.090 --> 34:54.929
the second,

34:54.610 --> 34:59.790
♪ That's why you're always
covered in scars ♪

34:55.139 --> 34:56.050
the third—

34:58.500 --> 35:00.310
you never came back.

35:01.430 --> 35:05.040
♪ If darkness can stop the pain ♪

35:03.560 --> 35:04.810
But even so,

35:05.350 --> 35:10.540
♪ I'll let you sleep a bit longer ♪

35:05.650 --> 35:06.610
I still went back

35:06.610 --> 35:08.220
to the place we used to live

35:08.970 --> 35:10.420
and posted my contact info

35:10.420 --> 35:12.030
on the bulletin board in the stairwell.

35:12.030 --> 35:16.040
♪ I'll stay by your side tonight ♪

35:12.530 --> 35:13.730
Because I was afraid.

35:15.080 --> 35:18.010
I was afraid that one day
you might suddenly come back

35:18.920 --> 35:24.040
♪ I want to meet the dusk with you ♪

35:18.990 --> 35:20.720
and wouldn't be able to find me.

35:24.400 --> 35:28.280
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

35:29.050 --> 35:35.090
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

35:35.540 --> 35:39.190
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

35:37.920 --> 35:39.840
I really hated tutoring classes

35:39.680 --> 35:43.780
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

35:39.860 --> 35:41.300
and doing homework,

35:42.210 --> 35:44.690
but I didn't dare slack off for a moment.

35:44.120 --> 35:48.290
♪ But I'm still waiting
for every dawn and dusk ♪

35:46.790 --> 35:48.130
I'm worried

35:48.310 --> 35:52.250
♪ To run towards you again ♪

35:48.370 --> 35:50.300
afraid that if you came back one day

35:50.510 --> 35:52.270
and saw how terrible my grades were,

35:52.270 --> 35:59.790
♪ Even if I hug you for a moment ♪

35:52.310 --> 35:54.150
you'd be disappointed in me.

36:00.290 --> 36:02.770
Today I saw you fighting in the ring.

36:03.660 --> 36:04.970
You were hurt—

36:05.470 --> 36:07.330
your hands were covered in blood.

36:07.500 --> 36:08.500
I was worried...

36:09.470 --> 36:10.610
I was worried that one day

36:10.610 --> 36:13.170
you might not even be able
to write anymore.

36:14.330 --> 36:16.210
I even bought you a fountain pen.

36:16.270 --> 36:20.510
♪ Meet the dusk with you ♪

36:18.220 --> 36:19.220
But now it seems

36:19.650 --> 36:21.700
you probably don't need it anymore.

36:21.000 --> 36:24.760
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

36:25.410 --> 36:30.480
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

36:32.110 --> 36:35.760
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

36:35.870 --> 36:40.260
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

36:40.320 --> 36:42.320
♪ But I'm still waiting ♪

36:42.600 --> 36:44.260
♪ For every dawn and dusk ♪

36:44.280 --> 36:48.210
♪ To run towards you again ♪

36:45.890 --> 36:47.410
Now I understand.

36:48.580 --> 36:52.260
♪ Until I can embrace you ♪

36:49.570 --> 36:51.030
I was just fooling myself.

36:52.180 --> 36:53.490
I shouldn't have come.

36:54.470 --> 36:57.760
♪ For a lifetime ♪

36:56.030 --> 36:56.800
Tomorrow...

36:57.140 --> 36:59.340
Tomorrow I'll trouble you one last time

36:59.710 --> 37:01.110
to take me to the airport.

37:01.310 --> 37:03.170
I'm going back to China tomorrow.

37:03.860 --> 37:06.260
I'll never do something this stupid again.

37:18.060 --> 37:19.920
Can't you at least say something?

37:20.190 --> 37:20.900
Sit tight.

37:38.270 --> 37:39.330
What's happening?

37:39.810 --> 37:40.610
Hold on tight.

38:43.040 --> 38:46.300
Look at this horizontal stroke.
You need to keep it steady.

38:47.030 --> 38:48.510
Yes, it needs to be steady.

38:48.780 --> 38:50.240
And this vertical stroke.

38:54.430 --> 38:56.830
You need to apply
some pressure here for it.

38:59.050 --> 39:00.980
Don't look at me. Focus on writing.

39:20.800 --> 39:30.170
[Mu]
